title: [Oasis, Storage]
description: Behind haphazardly constructed wooden shelves laden with pottery, woven baskets and open crates cover much of the hard-packed sand floor.  Flowers and herbs are hung on drying racks overhead, and bundles of rare hides are neatly arranged on a low table beside a tent flap.
room.location: between Wehnimer's Landing and Zul Logoth
